{
  "date_key": "2026-03-16",
  "date_cn": "2026年03月16日",
  "day_cn": "周一",
  "english": "<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#1a73e8\">职场与成功（Career, Ambition, Perseverance）</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;border-left:4px solid #0d47a1;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#0d47a1;font-size:15px\">【英文原文】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Hey, you look like you&#x27;re <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">on cloud nine</span> today. What&#x27;s going on?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Dude, I finally got the promotion. I&#x27;ve been grinding it out for two straight years, and it actually paid off. I&#x27;m gonna be leading the whole product team starting next month.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">No way! That&#x27;s huge. Honestly, you totally deserve it. I know you&#x27;ve been putting in the work while everyone else was just phoning it in.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yeah, there were times I wanted to quit, not gonna lie. Especially last summer when they passed me over for that senior role. I was so close to throwing in the towel.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I remember that. You were <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">pretty bummed out</span>. But you didn&#x27;t let it get to you. You just kept your head down and kept hustling.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Exactly. My mentor told me, &quot;Don&#x27;t burn bridges, just level up.&quot; So I pivoted, took on that cross-functional project nobody wanted, and used it to make a name for myself.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Smart move. That project was a heavy lift, though. I heard your team was basically running on fumes by the end of Q3.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Oh, totally. But we pulled it off somehow. And that&#x27;s what caught the director&#x27;s eye. She told me I really moved the needle on revenue, and that&#x27;s when things started falling into place.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">See, that&#x27;s the thing — you didn&#x27;t just climb the ladder, you built your own lane. Most people around here are just going through the motions, clocking in and clocking out.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">For real. And look, I&#x27;m not trying to rest on my laurels. This promotion is just a stepping stone. I want to eventually call the shots on company strategy, maybe even shoot for VP in a few years.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I have zero doubt you&#x27;ll get there. You&#x27;ve got the drive. Just don&#x27;t burn yourself out along the way, alright?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Appreciate that, man. I&#x27;ll pace myself. But yeah — sky&#x27;s the limit.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;border-left:4px solid #1b5e20;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1b5e20;font-size:15px\">【中文翻译】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">嘿，你今天看起来<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">高兴得不得了</span>啊。怎么了？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哥们，我终于升职了。我整整拼了两年（grinding it out），终于有回报了。下个月开始我要带领整个产品团队了。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">不会吧！太牛了。说实话，你完全配得上。我知道你一直在努力，而别人都在敷衍了事（phoning it in）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">是啊，说实话有好几次我都想放弃。尤其去年夏天那个高级职位没给我的时候，我差一点就认输不干了（throwing in the towel）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">我记得。你当时<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">挺郁闷的</span>。但你没让那件事击垮自己。你就是埋头苦干、一直拼（kept hustling）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">没错。我的导师跟我说：&quot;别烧断关系（don&#x27;t burn bridges），专注提升自己。&quot;所以我调整方向（pivoted），接手了那个没人想碰的跨部门项目，借此让自己闯出了名声（make a name for myself）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">聪明的做法。不过那个项目确实很吃力。我听说你的团队到第三季度末基本上已经精疲力竭了（running on fumes）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">完全是。但我们还是搞成了。这就是引起总监注意的原因。她跟我说我确实在收入方面产生了实质性影响（moved the needle），然后一切就开始水到渠成了（falling into place）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">你看，关键就在这儿——你不只是在按部就班地往上爬（climb the ladder），你是开辟了自己的赛道（built your own lane）。这里大多数人只是做做样子混日子（going through the motions），打卡上班打卡下班。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">确实。而且，我也不打算吃老本（rest on my laurels）。这次升职只是一个跳板（stepping stone）。我最终想要在公司战略上拍板做主（call the shots），甚至几年内冲一下副总裁。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">我完全相信你能做到。你有那股冲劲。只是别把自己累垮了（burn yourself out），行吗？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">谢了，兄弟。我会控制节奏的。但是——没有什么不可能（sky&#x27;s the limit）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f3e5f5;border-left:4px solid #4a148c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#4a148c;font-size:15px\">【本日表达列表】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">01.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>grind it out</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 咬牙坚持做，长期埋头苦干</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容在工作或学习中长时间艰苦努力、不放弃</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">02.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>phone it in</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 敷衍了事，不用心做</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容同事或员工消极怠工、走过场</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">03.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>throw in the towel</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 认输，放弃</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全球通用（源自拳击）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 面对困境时表达想要放弃的念头</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">04.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>burn bridges</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 断绝后路，搞砸人际关系</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 职场中提醒人离职或发生冲突时不要得罪人</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">05.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>make a name for yourself</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 闯出名声，建立个人声誉</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容通过出色表现让自己被认可</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">06.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>running on fumes</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 精疲力竭仍在硬撑（像车快没油了还在跑）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容团队或个人在高压项目尾声筋疲力尽</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">07.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>move the needle</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 产生实质性影响，推动指标变化</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国职场</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 汇报工作成果时强调真正带来了可衡量的改变</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">08.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>build your own lane</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 开辟自己的赛道，走出独特的路</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国（尤其创业/职场文化）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 鼓励人不要随大流，找到自己的差异化优势</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">09.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>rest on your laurels</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 吃老本，躺在过去的功劳簿上</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 提醒自己或他人不要因过去的成功而停滞不前</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">10.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>call the shots</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 拍板做主，掌握决策权</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容在团队或公司中拥有最终决定权的角色</span></td></tr></table>",
  "beauty": "<div style=\"background:#fce4ec;border-left:4px solid #e91e8c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#c2185b;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#c2185b\">底妆技巧 · 橄榄皮圆脸的&quot;透亮小脸&quot;底妆法</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 1｜妆前养肤——给厚角质一个柔滑起点</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>前一晚</strong>：使用含 5% 果酸（AHA）或低浓度水杨酸的去角质精华，软化老废角质，让第二天底妆更服帖。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>当日早间</strong>：洁面后依次上——</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\">轻薄保湿精华（含烟酰胺或维 C 衍生物，帮助提亮黄暗底色）</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\">控油保湿乳（T 区薄涂、两颊正常用量）</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\">等待 3-5 分钟完全吸收后再上妆前</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 2｜妆前乳——分区&quot;色彩校正&quot;</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">圆脸 + 橄榄皮需要 <strong>两支妆前</strong> 分区使用：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 区域 | 妆前选择 | 作用 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|----------|------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>全脸</strong> | 控油柔焦妆前（透明/肤色） | 填平毛孔、减少油光 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>面中（两颊、鼻梁、额心）</strong> | <strong>蜜桃色/杏粉色调妆前</strong> | 中和橄榄底的灰绿暗沉，提升气色 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; ⚠️ 避开紫色隔离！紫调在橄榄皮上会显得更灰更脏。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 3｜粉底——选对色调是灵魂</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🔑 色调选择核心法则</div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">橄榄皮 ≠ 黄皮。<strong>选&quot;黄调偏暖中性&quot;</strong> 的粉底色号——带一点点绿灰底调才不会在脸上&quot;浮&quot;出一层橘色面具。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">上妆手法（圆脸专属）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>工具</strong>：用扁头粉底刷先铺开，再用微湿美妆蛋弹压拍匀（比纯蛋上妆遮盖力更好，适合大毛孔）。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>用量策略——中间厚、四周薄</strong>：</span></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>面中三角区（眼下→鼻翼→嘴角）给足量，遮暗沉，打造&quot;聚光感&quot;。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>脸部外轮廓（太阳穴→腮帮→下颌角）粉底薄薄带过即可，<strong>留出后续修容的空间</strong>，从底妆阶段就开始「视觉收窄」。</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>下巴方向</strong>：将粉底往下巴尖方向多延伸 1cm 并晕开到下颌线，制造&quot;脸部重心下移→视觉拉长&quot;的效果。</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 4｜遮瑕——精准点杀</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>黑眼圈</strong>：用偏蜜桃/三文鱼色遮瑕打底中和青灰色，再叠一层肤色遮瑕。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>毛孔/痘印</strong>：选膏状高遮遮瑕，用小号刷&quot;按压填入&quot;而非涂抹，避免拉扯毛孔。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>法令纹区域</strong>：薄薄提亮，圆脸面中会有&quot;肉感折痕&quot;，这一步帮你视觉减龄。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">Step 5｜定妆——圆脸の「瘦脸定妆法」</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">这是很多人忽略的小心机：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>T 区 + 面中</strong>：散粉用粉扑按压定妆 → 控油、雾面、缩毛孔。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>苹果肌以下→腮帮</strong>：用大号散粉刷轻轻扫 → 保留一点&quot;皮肤质感&quot;，避免全雾面显脸大显平。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>鼻梁、眉骨下方、下巴尖</strong>：不定妆或极薄定妆 → 保留光泽感，制造纵向&quot;一条光&quot;，视觉拉长脸型。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; 夏季或大油田：最后距脸 30cm 喷一层定妆喷雾，用手轻拍至半干。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">💡 针对你的肤质/脸型特别提醒</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>角质偏厚</strong>：底妆再好也架不住起皮卡粉。坚持每周 1-2 次温和去角质是底妆服帖的前提。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>毛孔偏大</strong>：上粉底前可在鼻翼/两颊毛孔区域额外叠一层&quot;毛孔隐形&quot;硅基妆前，用指腹按压填充。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>圆脸底妆雷区</strong>：</span></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>❌ 全脸均匀同一厚度粉底（会让脸看起来像一个平面大饼）</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>❌ 选太白的粉底试图&quot;提亮&quot;（橄榄皮白一号会灰、白两号会假面）</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>✅ 准确匹配或只深半个色号，靠妆前和局部提亮来解决暗沉</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🎨 产品 / 色号推荐</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">妆前乳</div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 产品 | 推荐理由 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|----------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>MAKE UP FOR EVER STEP 1 柔焦妆前（#3 蜜桃色）</strong> | 专为暗沉肌设计，杏粉调中和灰绿，不挑橄榄皮 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>HOURGLASS Veil 矿物妆前</strong> | 顶级柔焦填毛孔，控油持久，无色适合叠加使用 |</p>",
  "research": "<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 1</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">HAO YANG, Joseph Foley</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Translanguaging as Interactional Resources Employed by Students in EFL Student-Led Group Task Interaction</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Journal of English Language and Linguistics</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">This study aimed to investigate the strategies used by students during group tasks in the EFL classroom. The study focused on translanguaging as one of the strategies to facilitate communication and interaction among students. The data was collected by recording the classroom discussions of a focused group in an EFL class at a Chinese university over three hours. The analysis was carried out using…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文与<strong>方向二（课堂互动与中介）</strong>高度相关：研究聚焦EFL课堂中学生主导的小组任务互动，采用会话分析方法考察translanguaging作为互动资源的使用策略，与用户关注的translanguaging、peer interaction主题直接对应。此外，研究情境设在中国大学外语课堂，虽非CSL但其关于同伴互动中语言协商与意义建构的发现可为CSL课堂中的translanguaging实践及语言相关片段（LRE）研究提供方法论和理论参照。</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.62819/jel.2024.145\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.62819/jel.2024.145</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 2</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Richard Kern</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Twenty‐first century technologies and language education: Charting a path forward</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Modern Language Journal</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">54 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">The COVID-19 pandemic, necessitating remote instruction in the vast majority of educational institutions around the world, put technology squarely at the center of language learning and teaching. Virtually all teaching and learning was mediated by Zoom or similar videoconferencing platforms. Students could see one another&#x27;s faces (rather than the backs of their peers’ heads), but they could also c…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">这篇论文探讨21世纪技术对语言教育的影响，涉及远程教学中的课堂互动模式变革（如Zoom小组讨论、聊天窗口作为交际渠道），与【方向二】课堂互动与中介研究相关，尤其是技术中介下的同伴互动（peer interaction）及多模态交际资源的运用，可延伸至translanguaging在数字环境中的实践。此外，技术变革对教学实践的制度性影响也与【方向三】教师在新教学环境中的情感劳动与脆弱性议题存在潜在关联，例如教师在技术中介教</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1111/modl.12924\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1111/modl.12924</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 3</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Kevin W. H. Tai</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Translanguaging as Inclusive Pedagogical Practices in English-Medium Instruction Science and Mathematics Classrooms for Linguistically and Culturally Diverse Students</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Research in Science Education</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2021</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">119 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Abstract In English-medium instruction (EMI), English-as-a-second-language students will learn all/some subjects through English. Although there are a considerable number of studies which explore classroom interaction in Hong Kong (HK) secondary EMI schools, few studies have investigated EMI lessons which involve South Asian ethnic minorised students. These students share different linguistic and …</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文聚焦于EMI课堂中translanguaging作为包容性教学策略的运用，并采用多模态会话分析考察课堂互动，与<strong>方向二</strong>（CSL课堂互动与translanguaging）高度相关，尤其在translanguaging的理论框架和课堂互动分析方法上形成直接对话。同时，研究关注少数族裔学生在语言文化多样性背景下的学习体验，涉及语言权力与公平议题，与<strong>方向一</strong>中语言权力及认知不公正（epistemic injustice）的关切相呼应，也为理解制度化语言政策对边缘化群体的影响</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/s11165-021-10018-6\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1007/s11165-021-10018-6</a></td></tr></table>\n</div>"
}